          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "title": "No hangover, no headache",
            "body": "Tried [Kanbae] Alcohol Defence Capsules and they worked great for me! Took two before drinking and two after - woke up with no hangover, no headache, and no bloating. Love that it’s made with natural ingredients and gentle on the stomach. Worth a try if you’re prone to hangovers or Asian flush.sd",
